  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/wearables/\" rel=\"tag\">佩戴产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/06/visualized-history-of-augmented-and-virtual-reality-eyewear/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/livedsc050882.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n最近 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/GoogleGlass/\">Google Glass</a> 的新闻传得很火热，但别忘记其实已有不少前人开发过类似的增强实境及虚拟现实头戴装置。主站的编辑刚刚去过美国加州 Santa Clara 的 Augmented World Expo 走了一圈，在展场里竟发现了一列历来出现过的增强实境及虚拟现实头戴装置，当中有已经成了形的产品，亦有只是利用胶贴左贴右补的<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/05/15/visualized-google-glass-prototypes/\">原型机</a>，其中当然不乏大家都认识的 Google Glass，只是大家又可以认出多少来自其他公司的装置呢？不用多说，进入图集猜猜看吧。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/a-history-of-augmented-and-virtual-reality-headsets-0/\">A history of augmented and virtual reality headsets</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/a-history-of-augmented-and-virtual-reality-headsets-0/5938376/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/dsc05051_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/a-history-of-augmented-and-virtual-reality-headsets-0/5938377/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/dsc05053_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/a-history-of-augmented-and-virtual-reality-headsets-0/5938378/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/dsc05054_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/a-history-of-augmented-and-virtual-reality-headsets-0/5938379/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/dsc05055_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/a-history-of-augmented-and-virtual-reality-headsets-0/5938380/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn